  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK1063">
<l>iṉmai yiṭumpai yirantutīr vāmeṉṉum </l>
<l>vaṉmaiyiṉ vaṉpāṭṭa til</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>There is no greater folly than the boldness with which one seeks to remedy the evils of poverty by begging (rather than by working).</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
